{
  "stem": "3631.4",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I cannot tell you I went to somebody and said, hey, put me on Schindler's list, and they said, well, give me $10,000, I'll put you on Schindler's list.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "That didn't exist.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, through the office, we-- we heard.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I want to point out that that was not necessarily the salvation-- Schindler's list.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We did not really know whether this would succeed or not.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Of course, it did not exist in the annals of-- of the concentration camp that a factory could request 1,000 people by name.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They could say, I want 50 electricians and 100 plumbers.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But they said I want Jack Miller and Max Smith-- this did not exist.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And-- and that was Schindler's greatest accomplishment, that he was able to do this.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He said, these are-- he had to make ammunition.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He had to build up an ammunition factory.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "These are his people.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "These are the people who are qualified to do this job.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And if the German government wants Schindler to do-- to do his job for the German army, he needs these people.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I guess, with the support of diamonds and liquor and so on, this went over.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "He had great trouble with the women, to getting them out, because the-- the commandant in Auschwitz didn't know of-- didn't want to know of it.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And I heard-- whether it's true are not, I don't know-- that he had to go to Berlin and pull strings there, and to finally get them out.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We left October 15th, my father and I.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We went to Gross-Rosen, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] an extermination camp in eastern Germany, in which during the war I understand one and a half million people were killed.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We spent three days there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We got there.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We were received with beating.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
